#. type: YAML Front Matter
#: upstream/_posts/2021-09-20-logicdrop-customer-story.adoc:3
msgid "How Quarkus Improved Logicdrop's Developer Experience and Process"
msgstr "QuarkusがLogicdropのデベロッパーエクスペリエンスとプロセスをどのように改善したか"

#. type: YAML Front Matter
#: upstream/_posts/2021-09-20-logicdrop-customer-story.adoc:4
msgid "2021-09-20"
msgstr "2021-09-20"

#. type: YAML Front Matter
